Bootstrap: docker
From: ubuntu:20.04

%post
    apt-get -y update && apt-get install -y python3 python3-pip
    pip3 install numpy pandas matplotlib seaborn pysam biopython
    # Example Python packages
    # Additional software installation commands here

%runscript
    exec python3 "$@"

%help
    This container runs a Python 3 environment with numpy and pandas installed.
